</select><P></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharafi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharafi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/10/02 9:31:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22695.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> For me personally i still prefer playing both.<br>
<br>
Sometime i just want to relax in a xp group and get a little Xp so i play my cleric. Other times i feel the need to Keel stuff so i go with my rogue. <br>
On raids i always play my cleric because unfortunatly i am a better cleric than a rogue and i can help more people playing my cleric.<br>
